  "elapsed_s": 245.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And since I didn't have no money, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I decided to try to get from this woman this fur coat, you know, to sell it, or to be exchanged for food, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So this [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Maria ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Nikichna, ?] who looked like a saint-- and was a saint.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So she went to this wife, and asked-- [INAUDIBLE] remember the name, Dr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Rachiborski. ?] And the Germans took him away, her husband, the doctor-- probably killed him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And she told her about this fur coat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And after a few persuasions, she gave [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Maria ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Nikichna ?] this fur coat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then we sold the-- the fur coat for a-- for flour, to make bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "For this helped to feed me [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So I stayed at-- the-- at the name, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "His name was Leonid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And one-- one was Zoya.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And one was Liza.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They gave-- they-- it was their house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So they gave me one room, that I could stay by myself there, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Did you have any false name, false papers?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they-- they were prepared to say, if somebody from the neighbors would see me and asked, they would say that I am a relative, that I came from another city, then-- a cousin or relative.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I suppose I looked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I'll tell you why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll tell you why I looked [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All right, so I was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we were preparing '43 to Christmas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Christmastime.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- they never-- religion-- they never asked me to change religion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They never-- this problem was nonexistent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but I was already participating in the preparation for Christmas, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He got some eggs and butter from the Germans and whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
